  <h1>About Neon Rewind Reviews</h1>

  <p>
    This site is a love letter to everything that made the 1980s feel electric: VHS tapes with
    hand-written labels, mall arcades glowing at midnight, paperback racks spinning at airport
    newsstands, and movie scores that sounded like they were beamed in from another dimension.
  </p>

  <p>
    Every review on this site tries to capture that vibe&mdash;not just what a book or movie is
    about, but how it <em>feels</em> to encounter it with 1980s eyes. Or to rediscover it now,
    through a neon&#8209;tinted rear-view mirror.
  </p>

  <p>
    Categories covered: <strong>80s Sci-Fi Flicks</strong>, <strong>Retro Rom-Coms</strong>,
    <strong>Cult Classics</strong>, and <strong>Paperbacks &amp; Pulp</strong>. New reviews
    added whenever the mood strikes.
  </p>

